{"tid":1178034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署後續行動 —- 聯校登報","createTime":"2019-05-30T06:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T16:24:44.000Z","uid":66753,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"da69b6cf39f41ec0f76438e1a9c1dea42ea79390","tid":1178034,"uid":66753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"都陸續有二百幾間學校發起聯署聲明<br />\n係時候集中力量 轟份頭版聯校聯署！<br />\n<br />\n部分學校發起人開咗個Facebook群組，<br />\n想gather返各院校聯署聲明發起人，採進進一步行動（好大機會係下星期聯合登頭版）<br />\n<br />\n錢唔急可以keep住籌款，但最緊要係多啲學校參與，應承登報，等我哋二百個校名轟上報紙頭版大大把車落政府度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到話好多學校都未有人入群討論，大家可以去林輝個post睇睇，叫相關發起人聯絡佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yoTPw6o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyoTPw6o.png&h=422fd651&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bty4kZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBty4kZK.png&h=6965f0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wnuSuS5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwnuSuS5.png&h=98b3501a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxQeJc6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxQeJc6.png&h=084d6a2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9f51525ced112a008a2a972a9cf519ac5a4646","tid":1178034,"uid":66753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"232599f1e8ad9c8c887ea52c3704f999e0dcc306","tid":1178034,"uid":66753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:56:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d97c8fb68593513a13b74df745b53f58dde6386","tid":1178034,"uid":66753,"like":0